These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, december, november
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, balloon-flower, dahlia
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, hamster, ferret
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, ebony, brown, orange
House: wooden, gothic-revival, cape-cod, ranch-style
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, montecristo, havana
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, cucumber, banana, tomato
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 6. the person eating lettuce is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person eating tomato is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person eating cucumber is the cape-cod house##1
13. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
14. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
15. the havana-smoker is the owner of the hamster##1
16. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
17. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | april       | november      | december       | february    |
| Flower         | tulip    | dahlia    | lily      | balloon-flower    |
| Pet           | ferret | cat       | hamster | horse     |
| Color   | emerald         | brown  | orange      | ebony     |
| House   | gothic-revival          | ranch-style     | cape-cod       | wooden |
| Cigar         | montecristo       | aristoff | havana       | tiparillo   |
| Food     | tomato     | banana  | cucumber         | lettuce   |

