.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
House: art-deco, cottage, farmhouse, townhouse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, sunflower, daffodil
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, march, july
City: prague, colone, marseilles, boston
4 different games are played: snooker, go, chess, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing, volleyball, cricket
 1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the right of the art-deco house##1
11. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
13. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
15. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
16. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
17. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| House          | farmhouse     | cottage     | art-deco      | townhouse  |
| Flower         | daffodil  | zinnia  | sunflower      | tulip |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | almond-milk     | milk | iced-tea        |
| Birthday   | september    | december        | march        | july        |
| City   | marseilles | prague | boston   | colone  |
| Game           | whist   | snooker       | go        | chess       |
| Sport     | lacrosse     | volleyball     | cricket       | rowing     |

