4 different games are played: poker, snooker, go, mah-jongg
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, american, french, russian
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, fuchsia, ebony, yellow
 1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 6. the french is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
10. the russian is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the russian##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
14. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
15. the person who growsdaffodil is the person playing mah-jongg##1
16. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the french##1
17. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

